<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200823/d45f7daaf83a460f8986bc80d5ce2e1a.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">覆盖上树叶，再压上石头。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200823/0f4e2046f1184f7395147d172c77cd3b.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">剩下的就是等待。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200823/18a96420dd274cf480f2acf6ee11a582.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">15分钟后，我们的船“司机”揭开石块“锅盖”，拿起香蕉扒开皮。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200823/a072f013d72b4e5292002e0415492949.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">思琪编导边吃边说：很好吃哦！这种香蕉需要煮熟去皮后食用，味道类似入口很干的蒸白薯。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200823/19cd62aba8d84cb0b66eb03dc765a91e.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">那棵枯树挺有特点。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200823/0f93db3154624009bd8f810755e72679.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200823/d16a24eaaed1419882f2afdd4c318848.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">船“司机”向那棵枯树走去。这么看那棵枯树并不大。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200823/fece6ab6ff5a47d8ab6cdd99a29a631b.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">蹭蹭几下就爬到枯树上。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200823/ecbebe33de354ddd9ab1605fe6142fb4.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">有人做参照物，就看出这颗枯树还是挺大的，好吧好吧，必须来个留影。</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200823/ac6cbd8e78074a0fbbecfd3a65d0dd02.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">来来来……拍一个。</span></img></p>
